## 6. ENDPOINTS DE L'API PROSPECTIVA

```
GET    /api/prospective/projects                           → Llista de projectes
POST   /api/prospective/projects                          → Crear projecte
GET    /api/prospective/projects/{id}                     → Obtenir projecte
PUT    /api/prospective/projects/{id}/variables           → Guardar variables
POST   /api/prospective/projects/{id}/micmac              → Calcular MIC-MAC
PUT    /api/prospective/projects/{id}/actors              → Guardar actors
PUT    /api/prospective/projects/{id}/objectives          → Guardar objectius MACTOR
POST   /api/prospective/projects/{id}/mactor              → Calcular MACTOR
PUT    /api/prospective/projects/{id}/components          → Guardar components morfològics
GET    /api/prospective/projects/{id}/scenarios/stream    → SSE streaming escenaris
GET    /api/prospective/projects/{id}/scenarios           → Escenaris guardats
```

